 ►Nstation_data_modThis module is used for outputing model results in a list of stations (not gridded arrays). The user needs to supply a list of stations with lat, lon values of each station. Data at a single point (I,J) that is closest to each station will be written to a file. No interpolation is made when a station is between two or more grid points.
In the output file, a 3D field will have a format of array(n1,n2) and a 2D field is array(n1) where n1 is number of stations and n2 is number of vertical levels or depths
